## Attribution Requirements

When using or distributing this software, you must:

1. **Give appropriate credit** by including:
   - The name "Tibia Assets Editor"
   - A link to the original repository
   - A link to this license
   - An indication if you modified the original work

2. **Example attribution:**
   ```
   This work is based on Tibia Assets Editor (https://github.com/seu-usuario/tibia-assets-editor)
   by Tibia Assets Editor Contributors, licensed under CC BY-NC-SA 4.0
   (https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/)
   ```

